    <description>
        <p>Easy Audio Sync is an audio library syncing and conversion utility. The intended use is syncing an audio library with many lossless files to a mobile device with limited storage.</p>
        <p>Features:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Custom FFmpeg-based audio transcoding engine</li>
          <li>Multithreaded operation for fast conversions</li>
          <li>4 lossy output codecs supported: MP3, AAC, Ogg Vorbis, and Opus</li>
          <li>Robust metadata parser ensures tags and cover art are correctly transferred when converting between different formats</li>
          <li>ReplayGain volume adjustments</li>
          <li>Destination folder cleaning (deleting files that no longer exist in the source)</li>
        </ul>
    </description>
